/></span></h2>

<p> Last Updated: {new Date(lastUpdate).toUTCString()} </p>
</Card>
</Col>

<Col span={6} >

<Card title="Total Deaths" bordered={false} hoverable
style={{ width: "100%" }}>

    <p> Total Deaths due to Covid-19: </p>
